    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defeat your opponents at the card table and uncover their secrets!</h2>TCA is a political, humorous card adventure game with charm. Discover the atmospheric (ballpoint pen) hand-drawn world and its inhabitants and collect lots of cards in the process! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169850/extras/1934fdf2dadd623c37e557fb730fee3c.poster.avif?t=1760108885\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169850/extras/1934fdf2dadd623c37e557fb730fee3c.webm?t=1760108885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169850/extras/1934fdf2dadd623c37e557fb730fee3c.mp4?t=1760108885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect cards and build a deck!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169850/extras/85c151b14e0eecbf3c59eb2dc49eb154.avif?t=1760108885\" width=800 height=450 /></span><br>Choose from many cards with different values and abilities to build your own deck!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Talk to characters and learn dark truths</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169850/extras/e568269e11f7106e9626e7c7d3cb35c4.avif?t=1760108885\" width=800 height=450 /></span><br>What lies behind the façade of the cozy small town? A demonic rat, a cult in the sewers and the impending end of the world. In between, the everyday madness of the present.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Find your very own strategy</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169850/extras/85c81e289186cf148a91b7d4ca3c6dc1.avif?t=1760108885\" width=800 height=450 /></span><br>Not every strategy leads to the goal. Combine different card types or specialize!",
